data.description: You don't want to miss out this opportunity! Corner lot Property with 4 bedrooms/2 bath home with three levels, a swimming pool and many upgrades done. Garage converted and also one bonus mother in law suite room . The house is located close to shopping, banks and restaurants. Tampa International Airport is about 15 min. Property is sold "as is" for the convenience of the sellers. Gorgeous home fully fenced giving you a lot of security and privacy. Community located in the Town 'N' Country. NO HOA NO CDD - .The Property is totally move in ready . Call now to make an appointment to see it before it's too late.
